_header: How the time that is past hath been spended
_description: On transience and mutability — three lines

BodLatTheD1.Transcription:
howh þe tyme that is paste hath ben spendetBe holde þe tyme
                    þat þou arte Inekaste & nowh amendetþer tyme þat
                    schal be laste at þi liffes ende
